      <scopecontent>
         <head>Scope and Content Information</head>
         <p>This addition to the Papers of Hardy Cross Dillard consists
         of miscellaneous materials found in the Law School in the
         spring of 1995. Of particular note are small notebooks and
         journals kept by Dillard before and during World War II, as
         well as notes and documents for 
         <title render="italic">McClanahan v. California Spray-Chemical
         Corporation</title>, a case in which Dillard represented the
         plaintiff before the Virginia Supreme Court.</p>
      </scopecontent>
